{"tid":1310576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB新聞先係文宣戰最大障礙","createTime":"2019-07-12T17:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T02:52:29.000Z","uid":36775,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf325b4439647300d53617862ed620d086d5f0c","tid":1310576,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:33:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TVB新聞抹黑抗爭者十分鐘已經贏連登仔幾日文宣</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>日日幫手扣血變咗白做</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣可集中攻擊TVB公信力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nTVB貴為香港最大台，83台新聞日日抹黑示威者<br />\n扮客觀中立持平報導新聞，新聞報導手法七三比<br />\n昆咗唔少中間派<br />\n<br />\n無可否認好多人資訊主要來自TVB 83台<br />\n中間班唔會主動上連登同睇黃嘅facebook page<br />\nTVB新聞抹黑10分鐘已經贏咗連登仔用幾日做嘅文宣<br />\n<br />\n中間派認為TVB新聞只要有提及反對意見=中立，好易被誤導<br />\n加埋信曬TVB講乜，唔會fact check，食思想殘廢餐<br />\n根據TVB偏頗陳述去做判斷就永遠不利我地<br />\n所以輿論戰日日比TVB幫手扣血，難吸收中間派甚至淺藍選民<br />\n<br />\n除咗比壓力TVB廣告商停止落廣告、del台之外<br />\n應該集中火力降低TVB新聞公信力，眨至公文商三報紙Level，報完都無人信<br />\n可以重點宣傳<br />\n<br />\n1.偏頗報導<br />\neg.女狀元意見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QL4NaEc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQL4NaEc.jpg&h=afd807af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.有概定立場<br />\n環球時報認證TVB有概定立場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uuYqGMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuuYqGMM.png&h=9e696c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.內部記者不滿高層維穩<br />\n雨革tvb記者聯署信，抗議袁花報導手法不中立，當中包括唔少知名記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1027301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1027301&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BQVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=dae15485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1027301&h=5d7c0c06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1027301</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣最後推介轉睇77台或99台新聞<br />\n<br />\n長遠要潛移默化TVB新聞有概定立場<br />\n搞到中間派同淺藍唔會盡信TVB新聞"},{"pid":"91fbfe1a27ae08065fe6c0372be076485d0e12fe","tid":1310576,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb01e6249a10146ecc2c1b311f15b22256797034","tid":1310576,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946491e6c8da9e937607e0d69dfc0b78f31dbf97","tid":1310576,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b9356a21b3058c1c94d3a31bc7accb11193ea9","tid":1310576,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe8022a2bfdbbdc8452ff9fc560c56f507abedf","tid":1310576,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6253e7ac55b1a125a927f64a8db56eb281345e3b","tid":1310576,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T23:54:05.000Z","msg":"恥與為伍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d8b413809419af1a2197a7cb77eac2cec9e4fd","tid":1310576,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T00:16:57.000Z","msg":"推，TVB 可恥"},{"pid":"ad9d9878a79d0aeb264b61489164d0fb1e1a1a14","tid":1310576,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T00:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm